Class.name: EasyCSP.Web.Client.ScriptDefinition
Class.Description: Holds in-line scripts in a stream until the page is rendered. Each script is given an id by the caller. When adding a script to the rendering queue, please use the parameters in that class to ensure proper placement of the script in the page.
